\id 2TI - Abureni
\h 2 A̠timoti
\toc3 2 A̠tim
\toc2 2 A̠timoti
\toc1 Wa̠leghemeni I̠wal A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m A̠timoti Bho̠
\mt2 Wa̠leghemeni I̠wal A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m
\mt1 A̠timoti
\mt2 Bho̠
\imt1 Otighom
\ip Apo̠l a̠nwuna̠ i̠sar rezin ya̠ i̠na atu̠n age̠ ma̠ a̠lebh onon agi̠o̠m A̠timoti d̠a̠ obhel bho̠.
\ip 1. I̠na ku̠ku̠m od̠i (4:10, 11); A̠filipai̠ 2:20.
\ip 2. Apo̠l aku̠nu̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ado̠l aso̠si̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ obhel ad̠agi̠an onon.
\ip 3. I̠na a̠ru ra̠ o̠ge̠ onigha̠ aso̠si̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ E̠fi̠so̠s bho̠.
\ip I̠na age̠ ma̠ a̠lebh onon ma̠ obhin onigha̠ ogbo irileghom aso̠si̠ omom amu̠m onon. I̠na a̠puru nyen ra̠tologha̠n d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ obhin ra̠d̠ire d̠o̠yo̠ oruom o̠yo̠ ma̠ igiel awa na̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ ozua̠n o̠yo̠, okunukun ra̠d̠ire ya̠ ubhin ozu e̠nam u̠le̠m bho̠. Ya̠a̠ idi ra̠d̠ire bho̠ ta̠ erue e̠ro̠ ma̠ idi a̠risisi d̠a̠ Ugba̠iny I̠zo̠ bho̠, d̠a̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠, sekina̠ ipa̠n ra̠d̠ire ya̠ ubhin ikpo a̠fugh d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ u̠ge̠. Apo̠l a̠kikiom A̠timoti ma̠ a̠kikiom ya̠ ilei abar, ma̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠mar o̠ro̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ogir ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st, na̠ one egbika̠ d̠a̠ i̠kparakpar ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ya̠ ta̠ eru bho̠. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ a̠ga̠i o̠di̠o̠ma bo̠, bha̠ i̠yar o̠nu̠r omel o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ obhel i̠kparama ado̠l. Agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ a̠sen a̠d̠ire onon bho̠, loghome ma̠a̠, anwa na̠ a̠sen ekunuguma̠ ikpo a̠fugh ta̠ obom o̠ni̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ onon, na̠ ekunuguma̠ ikpo a̠fugh ya̠ u̠ge̠ unigha̠ ma̠ A̠timoti na̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ awa ta̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m Akrai̠st bho̠.
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠
\io1 Ali̠se̠bh ta̠ Apo̠l ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠timoti \ior (1:1-5) \ior*
\io1 Ogir ya̠ Apo̠l a̠ruom A̠timoti ma̠ ogir \ior (2:6-13)\ior*
\io1 I̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ u̠gba umutiom agu̠o̠ a̠ga̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ aro̠ \ior (2:3-26)\ior*
\io1 Ab̠agh e̠mu̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru wa̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ \ior (3:1-17) \ior*
\io1 Ekunuguma̠ ikpo a̠fugh ta̠ Apo̠l \ior (4:1-22)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Ibheleguma̠ ta̠ Apo̠l
\p 
\v 1 Ami̠ Apo̠l o̠ni̠ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st d̠a̠ i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, wa̠ uruom o̠gba a̠ghud̠um ogua̠n wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s o̠sasaragi̠ bho̠,
\v 2 na̠ age̠ na̠ a̠ruom anwa A̠timoti o̠nyi̠ ed̠igh ologi d̠ami̠. E̠ne̠ghe̠, igbirigbir, na̠ ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar e̠ro̠ na̠ anwa.
\s1 Ali̠se̠bh na̠ O̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ologi
\p 
\v 3 Ami̠ na̠ ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin e̠b̠ab̠ala eloghoma̠n na̠ ako̠l bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ igir bho̠. Ami̠ na̠ ka̠ ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ kigiel kigiel ami̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an igboloma̠ ma̠ anwa d̠a̠ ra̠siseiny d̠ami̠ ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n.
\v 4 Ami̠ na̠ aru̠ru̠an agu̠o̠ anwa ibhin ileghe bho̠ sa̠ na̠ ebhir ami̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh oyom, b̠o̠ka̠ ologi d̠ami̠ a̠muzo na̠ ibo ma̠ igiel i̠yar ta̠ ozua̠n.
\v 5 Ami̠ na̠ aru̠ru̠an na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ igielake̠ onweni a̠ko d̠oyom A̠luwis na̠ onweni d̠oyom A̠yunasi̠, sa̠ ami̠ i̠mar ima̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ od̠i nyen d̠a̠ ozu d̠oyom.
\v 6 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠nimeta̠n anwa ma̠ o̠so̠so̠me̠ni̠ enigha̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠b̠eton a̠nigha̠ nyam igiel bho̠ ami̠ i̠gbamagi̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ ozu d̠oyom bho̠.
\v 7 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ onigha̠ d̠o̠ i̠yar e̠mu̠gh a̠rugugu na̠ alu̠ku̠ a̠d̠ien, ya̠a̠, ola̠ a̠limon, na̠ etula̠n, na̠ osibhom ozu.
\v 8 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ko oghil ari̠ghe̠l ma̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar onigha̠ ipa̠n ogbo. Ko odin nyen ma̠a̠ u̠du̠o̠m ami̠ ma̠ ikoli ma̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠, ma̠ a̠ghil ari̠ghe̠l osen ami̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ bhine ma̠ a̠limon ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam bho̠ ma̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ami̠ ma̠ a̠gbika̠ ma̠ ebula̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠.
\v 9 A̠zib̠a̠ a̠tenemeni i̠yar sa̠ aso̠n i̠yar ma̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um e̠b̠ab̠ala. Abar ola̠ i̠yar ugir ola̠ akpe̠ i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ i̠nye̠n bo̠, ya̠a̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ okpon igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠. Kisa̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, i̠na ato̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st o̠te̠i̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 10 I̠se̠n bha̠ ubhin eruoma̠ ta̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s oleriom i̠yar e̠ne̠ghe̠ bho̠. I̠na ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ omugh, ma̠ i̠yar o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ya̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠ruom i̠yar bho̠ o̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um, na̠ ozu ola̠ ko omugh mu.
\v 11 Sa̠ u̠so̠n ami̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ asasaragi̠, na̠ o̠ni̠ogir, na̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠.
\v 12 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh nyen ali̠gam a̠ruzu i̠nye̠n bho̠. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ami̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l, ezin bho̠ ami̠ a̠loghom i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ ami̠ id̠umom bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠kponom abar ola̠ ub̠eton u̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ tu̠tu̠n ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.
\v 13 Sibhe ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa i̠mu̠gho̠n d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠ ma̠ akparame̠ni̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. Bhine d̠a̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi na̠ etula̠n ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s ma̠ a̠gir.
\v 14 Mare̠ ma̠ a̠kponom ob̠eb̠i abar wa̠ ub̠eton u̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠limon ta̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ rologi d̠a̠ i̠yar bho̠.
\v 15 Anwa a̠loghom ma̠a̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Esia̠ na̠ eghel ami̠, sa̠ A̠figelus na̠ Ahe̠mo̠ze̠ne̠s eka̠ id̠igh ani̠.
\v 16 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠kpon igbirigbir Onisiforus na̠ eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa iguri gha̠n i̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi d̠ami̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa odin d̠o̠ ma̠a̠ ami̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ikoli be̠le̠ni̠ eghil ari̠ghe̠l.
\v 17 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠ru d̠a̠ A̠rom bho̠, i̠na abho̠ro̠ghan ami̠ kesi kesi tu̠tu̠n i̠na abi̠gh ami̠.
\v 18 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠kpon Onisiforus igbirigbir d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠. Anwa a̠loghom e̠mi̠ agu̠o̠ Onisiforus a̠bhin alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo re̠kal d̠a̠ E̠fi̠so̠s.
\c 2
\s1 Ob̠eb̠i O̠ni̠e̠gham ta̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, anwa o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, kpo̠ ma̠ a̠luzu d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s bho̠.
\v 2 Bhine ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa i̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠ ami̠ i̠gba d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ obhin ob̠em ologi ma̠a̠ awa ta̠ erue ani̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom.
\v 3 D̠ighe na̠ ami̠ ma̠ a̠gbika̠ ma̠ egbika̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠e̠gham ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s.
\v 4 O̠ni̠e̠gham na̠ o̠ko̠mo̠gi̠an gha̠n d̠o̠ na̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo-e̠gham, ka̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a bha̠ ko od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠-e̠gham bho̠ ma̠ ologi.
\v 5 Odi abar eka̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠pigia̠n eghil, ko orue d̠o̠ ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ ozuom i̠na ma̠ eghoi, a̠ten ka̠ i̠na atu̠o̠no̠m i̠to̠to̠gi̠ a̠pigia̠n bho̠.
\v 6 Sa̠ od̠i ma̠ ola̠, od̠ighi ma̠ ari̠si̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n na̠ a̠gir ogir ibom bho̠, akpe̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.
\v 7 Ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam bho̠. Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam o̠mu̠gho̠nyan eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n.
\v 8 Guri d̠a̠ ologi d̠oyom ma̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st wa̠ ub̠eton d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ ma̠ odi o̠nyi̠ i̠sabh ikpele ta̠ O̠li̠le̠ma A̠devidi. Onon Ob̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba wa̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ asasaragi̠ bho̠.
\v 9 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh ali̠gam ozu na̠ ate̠i̠ esi ola̠ na̠ o̠du̠gi̠ ami̠ ma̠ rikoli ma̠ agu̠o̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh. Ya̠a̠, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ abar ola̠ ta̠ orue o̠du̠o̠m ikoli d̠o̠.
\v 10 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ na̠ a̠ne kabar kabar, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ aso̠n bho̠ e̠te̠i̠ itenemeni d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s na̠ isosorogia̠n ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠.
\v 11 Onon o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ola̠ a̠lei abar ola̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠,
\q1 “Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar od̠igh na̠ i̠na omugh,
\q2 i̠yar ta̠ orugha̠n i̠na nyen.
\q1 
\v 12 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar one ma̠ a̠ma̠ne,\x - \xo 2:12 \xt A̠rom 6:8\x*
\q2 bha̠ i̠yar ta̠ od̠igh na̠ i̠na orileghom irileghom d̠o̠yo̠,
\q1 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar o̠ku̠a i̠na,
\q2 sa̠ i̠na ta̠ aku̠a i̠yar nyen.
\q1 
\v 13 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠yar usibh d̠o̠ ma̠ ogua̠n,
\q2 i̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠sibh ogua̠n,
\q2 ezin bho̠ i̠na ko orue d̠o̠ aku̠a ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠.”\x - \xo 2:13 \xt A̠rom 3:3\x*
\s1 O̠ni̠ogir wa̠ na̠ o̠da obhin bho̠
\p 
\v 14 Nimeta̠ne ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, ma̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ akparame̠ni̠ ma̠ agba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, awa e̠we̠le̠man aku̠anan ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh. Aku̠anan i̠ye̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠o̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nagha bho̠.
\v 15 Wia̠ne ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ ada ma̠ anwa a̠bhin agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ogir ola̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ezin ola̠ odin oghil ari̠ghe̠l, ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin ya̠ igielake̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠.
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, ghele ma̠ a̠fugh i̠te̠i̠ na̠ i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ya̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi, ezin bho̠ i̠ye̠ na̠ eb̠uimeni ma̠ i̠karabh d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠, sa̠ na̠ esigimeni ma̠ o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 17 Ta̠ obhin o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠awa i̠ye̠ o̠tu̠o̠m e̠ke̠te̠ ola̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠e na̠ are̠gh d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠. Ahi̠me̠ni̠o̠s na̠ A̠filetos na̠ erugh ado̠l i̠ye̠.
\v 18 Awa na̠ emel e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠ga̠i eten bho̠, sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ na̠ a̠mite a̠ten, obha̠ sa̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ a̠d̠izo ogbo.
\v 19 Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ade̠ ma̠ o̠kparakpar o̠de̠o̠ma ola̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠ onu o̠si̠ghe̠, sa̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠loghom ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ o̠yo̠ bho̠.”\x - \xo 2:19 \xt O̠wal 16:5\x* O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, “Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠sen a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ghel i̠karabh.”
\p 
\v 20 D̠a̠ otu ola̠ abu̠gh, a̠d̠ien kere kere i̠di̠ar a̠ma̠rugh otu od̠i, idi ubhin a̠silva̠ o̠le̠m, idi a̠gol, ipa̠n sa̠ ubhin iriren bo̠d̠o̠ i̠do̠gho̠l u̠le̠m. Idi ed̠igh edim, ya̠a̠ idi id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ edim.
\v 21 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni, o̠ni̠ ola̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh i̠ye̠ bha̠ oten abar edim, ola̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠doni a̠bhin a̠gir a̠d̠ien kere kere ib̠eb̠i ogir.
\v 22 Kpo ma̠ eghil ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠nyagh ikubh a̠nwunom. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ bha̠ra̠nome ma̠ a̠ghud̠um igielake̠, ologi ima̠ra̠, etula̠n na̠ ekima̠, ma̠ a̠bhin a̠rilogha̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebhin a̠ga̠i ologi na̠ esen Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.
\v 23 Si̠ghe̠ ma̠ ozu d̠oyom d̠a̠ raku̠anan ema̠ na̠ iya̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi, ezin bho̠ i̠ye̠ na̠ ekunugiom d̠a̠ o̠b̠e̠m.
\v 24 Ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠b̠u̠man o̠b̠e̠m. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, a̠bhin d̠a̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu na̠ d̠a̠ od̠ighi ib̠eb̠i na̠ e̠mar atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, a̠ne ma̠ a̠nwunom i̠kpalagi̠an.
\v 25 Bhine d̠a̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠damaghan anwa bho̠. Ka̠din A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rileghom awa ma̠ o̠wo̠l i̠se̠ otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh na̠ o̠mar ologhom eb̠la̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 26 Sa̠ awa ta̠ eloghoma̠n a̠ruzu e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠te̠ akpati̠ ta̠ Eru bho̠, wa̠ akpu̠o̠m awa a̠guri d̠a̠ ekpukpu i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\c 3
\s1 A̠ma̠rugh a̠nwunom d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠
\p 
\v 1 Loghome ma̠a̠ e̠kparama ado̠l ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠.
\v 2 Ezin bho̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ etula̠n a̠ruzu d̠awa na̠ otula̠n ikpoki, ebhubhugha̠, e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu, efugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠, sa̠ ko o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠, ko o̠se̠bh d̠o̠ ma̠ ali̠se̠bh, sa̠ ko orugh d̠o̠ ma̠ ado̠l igielake̠.
\v 3 A̠nwunom ta̠ erugh ado̠l ya̠ igbiriri ozu o̠to̠, sa̠ okpon o̠si̠ghe̠ a̠d̠ien ko̠ o̠ro̠ mu̠, ta̠ efugh i̠basi̠, ko osibhom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu, ta̠ e̠pi̠e̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠pi̠e̠gi̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠su̠a kabar kabar ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i.
\v 4 Awa ta̠ ewol iwola̠, e̠basi̠ ma̠ i̠basi̠, erugh ado̠l o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ a̠ruzu, etula̠n e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ otula̠n A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 5 Awa ta̠ ekue egir agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erugh iya̠ igielake̠, ya̠a̠, na̠ eghel a̠ga̠i a̠limon bho̠. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, sigima̠ ma̠ ozu d̠oyom d̠a̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠ku̠a.
\v 6 Idi awa na̠ e̠b̠o̠i̠ny na̠ ed̠ikighu d̠a̠ a̠rutu a̠nwunom na̠ eponoma̠ ma̠ anwani̠ idudugha̠n ologi ya̠ i̠karabh na̠ e̠ne̠mu̠o̠m bho̠, sa̠ na̠ erileghom awa na̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ebhiroma̠ i̠karabh.
\v 7 Anwani̠ i̠ye̠ bha̠, eb̠la̠ igiel od̠i d̠a̠ atu̠ghan, ya̠a̠ irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 8 A̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ Azane̠s na̠ Azambre̠s i̠damaghan A̠mozizi bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n eka̠ na̠ e̠damaghan a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠. Awa a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ i̠karabh i̠walama na̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ igunugha̠.
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, awa ko obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ esusula̠ d̠awa e̠gi̠ ma̠ egbeiny, ezin bho̠ ko obia̠ d̠o̠ sa̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠loghom a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ a̠gboloma̠ awa, ma̠ agu̠o̠ imutuma̠ ma̠ Azane̠s na̠ Azambre̠s bho̠.
\s1 A̠kikiom Ekunuguma̠ ya̠ Apo̠l a̠kikiom A̠timoti bho̠
\p 
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, anwa na̠ amar amu̠gho̠nyan atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠ami̠, na̠ a̠ma̠rugh d̠ami̠, na̠ ezin a̠ghud̠um d̠ami̠, na̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠ami̠, na̠ a̠ma̠ne d̠ami̠, na̠ etula̠n d̠ami̠, na̠ i̠kparagi̠o̠m d̠ami̠.
\v 11 Anwa a̠loghom a̠ponoma̠ egbika̠ ya̠ i̠te̠i̠ ami̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ i̠te̠i̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ Anti̠o̠k, na̠ Ikoni̠o̠m, na̠ A̠listara̠ bho̠. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ami̠ ane̠, sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠tenemeni ami̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu i̠ye̠.
\v 12 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ebhir obhin eb̠la̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ orugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s ta̠ abi̠gh a̠ponoma̠ egbika̠.
\v 13 Sa̠ ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom, na̠ ogbo igelemeni ta̠ egurom epeleni, sa̠ ta̠ egelemeni ma̠ a̠nwunom, sa̠ ta̠ ogelemeni awa nyen.
\v 14 Ya̠a̠ anwa, rughe ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa i̠tu̠ghan sa̠ anwa i̠mar ima̠ra̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ nyam bho̠.
\v 15 Loghome ma̠a̠, anwa iloghom O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ka̠ d̠a̠ i̠gbara d̠oyom, ya̠ inigha̠ nyam eloghomabar ya̠ na̠ ebhin itenemeni na̠ eru d̠a̠ o̠wo̠l oten ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s.
\v 16 A̠zib̠a̠ a̠b̠ugh a̠mutiom eb̠la̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhon ola̠ obhin o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, na̠ a̠kikiom, na̠ oselegi i̠di̠ar ya̠ obhon d̠o̠, na̠ atu̠ghan od̠igh e̠mu̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um igielake̠,
\v 17 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ta̠ amar a̠kokod̠ia̠n ogir eb̠la̠ ib̠eb̠i ogir.
\c 4
\s1 Ob̠eb̠i o̠gho̠r ola̠ o̠mar o̠ro̠
\p 
\v 1 Ami̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s wa̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um na̠ imumugh bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠li̠le̠ma d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠:
\v 2 Gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ obhel. Bhine d̠a̠ a̠ma̠ne na̠ a̠kikiom ma̠ a̠rubhugiom, na̠ o̠nyagh ra̠to, o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ rologi a̠nwunom.
\v 3 Obhel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ko o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ awa ta̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠karabh rebhiroma̠ ologi d̠awa, sa̠ ta̠ eko ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa ekitineni na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ ta̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ ebhir awa ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n.
\v 4 Sa̠ awa ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ sa̠ ta̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m asu̠gbagba id̠ud̠ul ya̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi.
\v 5 Ya̠a̠ anwa, kimeni ma̠ ozu d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar, ma̠ a̠ne ma̠ egbika̠, ma̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ o̠d̠u̠a esi oten esi, ma̠ a̠gir ogir wa̠ ubhelegi nyam ogir bho̠ ma̠ a̠muzoghod̠iom.
\v 6 I̠se̠n bha̠ na̠ ozu ma̠ asi̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠min i̠ko̠l, sa̠ obhel wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n.
\v 7 Ami̠ na̠ a̠we ma̠ ob̠eb̠i elobhiri, ami̠ na̠ amar a̠ghil eghil bho̠ ka̠ kunugiom, ami̠ na̠ a̠sibhom ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ka̠ a̠kunugiom.
\v 8 O̠ku̠a bha̠ i̠se̠n na̠ oguri ma̠ eghoi ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ osisa̠n ami̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ amu̠kpe̠ ola̠ ta̠ oleriom d̠a̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osobh Ase̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ami̠ a̠rugh iya̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠, osobhmase̠ igielake̠ bho̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, amu̠kpe̠ bho̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ enigha̠ ami̠ ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ani̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ itula̠n eruoma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\s1 Ekunuguma̠ a̠kikiom wa̠ Apo̠l a̠kikiom A̠timoti bho̠
\p 
\v 9 Wia̠ne ma̠ anu̠r a̠ru d̠ami̠ ma̠ obhel ola̠ ko obia̠ d̠o̠,
\v 10 ezin bho̠ Ade̠mas na̠ a̠ba̠ra̠ ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom amu̠m onon, sa̠ na̠ awe̠le̠man ami̠ a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ Ate̠saloni̠ka, A̠krise̠ns na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalesia̠, ya̠a̠ Atai̠to̠s na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Adalmatia̠.
\v 11 A̠luk ku̠ku̠m od̠i na̠ ami̠. Te̠ye̠ ma̠ Amaki̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ anwa a̠ru, ezin bho̠ i̠na ta̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ ogir d̠ami̠.
\v 12 Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠dila̠de a̠limon d̠ami̠ a̠ruom Ata̠i̠siku̠s oten o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ E̠fi̠so̠s.
\v 13 Igiel anwa na̠ a̠ru, bhine ma̠ akapa anyu̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i na̠ Akarpu̠s d̠a̠ A̠troa̠s bho̠. B̠arame̠ na̠ ra̠d̠ire bho̠, okunukun iya̠ ozu i̠nam bho̠.
\v 14 Ale̠kzanda o̠le̠ma i̠d̠i̠ar a̠rukurogh bho̠ a̠gir i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo re̠kal.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Raso̠r 28:4\x* Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ akpe̠ i̠na ma̠ ogir ya̠ i̠na a̠gir bho̠.
\v 15 Anwa eka̠ kpona̠ ma̠ a̠sigima̠ i̠na, ezin bho̠ i̠na adamaghan i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠i̠yar ibom.
\v 16 O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ agba d̠ami̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r igiel wa̠ ami̠ i̠gba ma̠ o̠nu̠ d̠a̠ iku wa̠ uler ami̠ bho̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ighel ami̠, ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠siseiny ma̠a̠ o̠wal d̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa.
\v 17 Ya̠a̠, Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ aro̠ na̠ ami̠ sa̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ akparame̠ni̠ ami̠, ma̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ omuzoghod̠iom onigha̠ eb̠la̠ Ibhebhia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ a̠tenemeni ami̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ odughunub̠agu̠ bho̠.
\v 18 Ya̠ga̠i, Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni ami̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar, a̠guri ami̠ ma̠ ola̠ eko ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny d̠o̠yo̠. Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a ma̠ amu̠m a̠ten amu̠m. Aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.
\s1 Ekunuguma̠ Ibheleguma̠
\p 
\v 19 Pura̠ne ma̠ A̠priska\f + \fr 4:19 \ft A̠priska: Onon opa̠n agu̠o̠ ola̠ na̠ obhelegi ma̠ A̠prisila̠ d̠a̠ Ogir 18:1-3\f* na̠ A̠kwila̠, na̠ eghun otu ta̠ Onisiforus.
\v 20 E̠rasto̠s aro̠ d̠a̠ Ako̠ri̠nt, ya̠a̠ ami̠ i̠we̠le̠man A̠trofimo̠s d̠a̠ A̠militus ezin bho̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ obhon d̠o̠.
\v 21 Wia̠ne ma̠ anu̠r a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ ami̠ kisa̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ obhel eb̠okum bho̠. A̠yubulus, na̠ Apu̠de̠ns, na̠ Alai̠no̠s, na̠ A̠kilodia̠, na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ bho̠ epura̠n anwa nyen.
\v 22 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ aro̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠oyom. E̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin.
